    "Headline": "Loop 'L' Service Delayed at Adams/Wabash",
    "ShortDescription": "Loop 'L' trains are standing at Adams/Wabash due to fire department activity. Crews working to restore service.",
    "FullDescription": {
      "#cdata-section": "<p>Loop &#39;L&#39;&nbsp; trains are standing at Adams/Wabash due to an fire department activity.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a result of the delayed train, Green Line trains will be rerouted to the outer Loop (trains will board and exit on the Brown Line platforms at <strong>Washington/Wells, Quincy/Wells, LaSalle/Van Buren, State/Van Buren, Adams/Wabash, Washington/Wabash, State/Lake and Clark/Lake.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At this time, also consider other service alternatives that may serve your trip, such as nearby bus routes, or using buses to other rail lines. These may include these shuttle buses:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li><strong>Brown Line shuttle buses will operate from Merchandise Mart to Clark/Lake</strong></li>\r\n\t<li><strong>Orange Line shuttle buses will operate from Halsted to Harold Washington Library-State/Van Buren</strong></li>\r\n\t<li><strong>Pink Line shuttle buses will operate from Polk to Ashland/Lake</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Personnel are working to restore service. Allow extra travel time.</p>\r\n"
    },
